---
description: Keep page headers concise without subtitle/lead text
globs: frontend/src/pages/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# No Page Subtitles

- In page header blocks, render only the main page title (`h1`).
- Do not add subtitle/description text under page title (`lead`, muted helper lines, or descriptive paragraphs under `h1`).
- If additional guidance is needed, place it in contextual UI blocks (filters, cards, hints), not in the page header.
